{"tid":1005034,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"低層員工新年竟然想去拜年 做啲無謂傳統節日習俗","createTime":"2019-02-02T02:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T14:47:19.000Z","uid":196627,"like":8,"dislike":150,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e714d4e6840aea0cb501cb3046d9272f021cef36","tid":1005034,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"話說新年就黎到<br />\n咁初一至初三係法定假期<br />\n理論上我公司係要俾你休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自願翻工呢<br />\n就合法嘅<br />\n竟然有低層同事<br />\n想唔自願繼續翻工<br />\n新年真係想去拜年！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢:<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢:唔好意思，我新年可能翻唔到黎幫手，想翻鄉下拜年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我:其他同事都話唔想放假，想自願繼續翻工，拜年真係咁重要？<br />\n<br />\n佢:法例規定我初一至初三有三日假期，點解我要繼續翻工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(竟敢同hr講法例，咁就同佢玩下喇)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我:我地公司就全部都係精英，全部人都好勤力，有同事平日翻五日之餘，仲自願翻埋星期六日同假期，一年翻足三百六十五日，做左三十年最近買到樓，你仲係低層員工，後生仔都捱唔起？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢:(冇野講)<br />\n<br />\n我:公司目的係利潤最大化，公司只需要對工作有熱誠既人，如果你真係捱唔起，我都明白你既未來意願嘅...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢:(都係冇野講)<br />\n<br />\n我:咁你嗰幾日休息下喇，自願翻工姐，冇人迫你嘅...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢:我嗰幾日，會自願繼續翻工<br />\n<br />\n佢講完最後一句<br />\n就頭Dup Dup<br />\n眼濕濕咁<br />\n然後垂頭喪氣咁走左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好心家陣啲年輕人<br />\n冇貢獻就想有回報<br />\n如果你肯捱足四五十年<br />\n買樓，唔再係夢想喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353da7f997acc6645e61e2006d949687ee70c23c","tid":1005034,"uid":154054,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:40:34.000Z","msg":"Hr死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假膠死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06324e242af87a7d070bc407752c5e9dc657dde0","tid":1005034,"uid":196627,"like":1,"dislike":59,"score":-58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"我個post完全唔係for笑<br />\n公司目的係利潤最大化<br />\n目的係警惕所有應徵者<br />\n幫大部分幼稚連登仔建立正確工作價值觀<br />\n要笑既可以正評後出翻去"},{"pid":"4f8a9d8a989c0dfaa53ccafe267002790d084d52","tid":1005034,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"Ho ball"},{"pid":"af64d343b309f92172868483463cbdd21ea1656d","tid":1005034,"uid":32783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"06324e242af87a7d070bc407752c5e9dc657dde0","tid":1005034,"uid":196627,"like":1,"dislike":59,"score":-58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"我個post完全唔係for笑<br />\n公司目的係利潤最大化<br />\n目的係警惕所有應徵者<br />\n幫大部分幼稚連登仔建立正確工作價值觀<br />\n要笑既可以正評後出翻去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:42:10.000Z","msg":"笑鳩你都要比正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a86f9d1de107b3a019ff7c9b053db6fd01819b8","tid":1005034,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:43:08.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔係話針對幾多十後<br />\n不過咁睇應該係00後黎"},{"pid":"c22a98a5bfc28eb3e59588c4a96600151e0090d1","tid":1005034,"uid":90820,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"成日出膠post<br />\n膠少陣啦<br />\n你就嚟膠壞腦㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca818bc292ff4d4b6136b1b5ca69708b20ced73","tid":1005034,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c22a98a5bfc28eb3e59588c4a96600151e0090d1","tid":1005034,"uid":90820,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"成日出膠post<br />\n膠少陣啦<br />\n你就嚟膠壞腦㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/no